title: [1508521049] Gordon Ramsay’s Fast Food: Crab & Chilli Pasta
description:
Fast food in Gordon Ramsay’s world involves fresh tagliatelle, crab meat, parsley and chilli. Just 10 minutes, and absolutely delicious.
